<HEADLINE> OAU Makes Donation to Addis Ababa Fine Arts </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, May 15 (Xinhua) -- The Organization of African
Unity (OAU) donated 5,000 US dollars to the Addis Ababa Fine Arts
School here today.
</P>
<P>
Presenting the cheque to Tadesse Belaineh, Director of the
school, OAU Secretary General Salim A. Salim recalled that a
pledge to this effect was made earlier this week when he
officially opened the on-going art exhibition by the students of
the school in the Congo Hall of the OAU General Secretariat.
</P>
<P>
