was an expression of the OAU's appreciation of the excellent art
work being taught by the school to the Ethiopian youth, adding
that Africa as a whole is likely to benefit from the tremendous
achievements of the school.
</P>
<P>
On his part, the director of the school expressed profound
gratitude and appreciation to the OAU for the timely donation which
he said would encourage the school significantly in carrying out
its goals and objectives, the release added.
