<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major Chinese Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, May 16 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 14 major
Chinese cities for the next 24 hours from 20:00 today to 20:00 on
May 17, issued by China's Central Meteorological Station at 17:00
today:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 13 degrees c., max. 30 degrees c., clear, strong
to moderate breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shenyang: min. 10 degrees c., max. 18 degrees c., drizzle, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin: min. 13 degrees c., max. 30 degrees c., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Xi'an: min. 15 degrees c., max. 30 degrees c., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Chengdu: min. 18 degrees c., max. 26 degrees c., drizzle to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Chongqing: min. 19 degrees c., max. 27 degrees c., overcast to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Kunming: min. 16 degrees c., max. 28 degrees c., clear to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Nanjing: min. 20 degrees c., max. 29 degrees c., overcast to
cloudy, gentle to moderate breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shanghai: min. 17 degrees c., max. 27 degrees c., cloudy to
clear, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Wuhan: min. 22 degrees c., max. 28 degrees c., overcast to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hangzhou: min. 18 degrees c., max. 28 degrees c., overcast to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Taipei: min. 20 degrees c., max. 28 degrees c., cloudy to
thunder showers, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Guangzhou: min. 24 degrees c., max. 30 degrees c., moderate
rain, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong: min. 26 degrees c., max. 30 degrees c., thunder
showers, calm to gentle breeze. 
</P>
