<HEADLINE> Medical Firms Merge in East China Province </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANGZHOU, May 16 (Xinhua) -- Three powerful pharmaceutical
firms merged together today in East China's Zhejiang Province, to
gain a cutting edge in an ever competitive market.
</P>
<P>
The Xinchang Pharmaceutical Shareholding Company, Ltd., which
ranks 18th in China's 50 most profitable pharmaceutical firms,
merged with two other firms to form the Zhejiang Pharmaceutical
Shareholding Company, Ltd..
</P>
<P>
