Barkley hit 20 and 12 for the Rockets, who again struggled from
3-point range -- 6-of-23. Houston is just 11-of-50 in the last two
games.
</P>
<P>
The Rockets have never beaten the Sonics in five playoff
series. Saturday's winner faces the Utah Jazz in the conference
finals.  
