unilateral move against the country, ASEAN should stick to its
decision on accepting Myanmar as a member, stressing that ASEAN
should pursue its 1995 decision on inclusion of Myanmar in ASEAN
and making clear that Thailand will not be swayed from adhering to
its position to support Myanmar in becoming an ASEAN member,
