benefits for the teachers, he added.
</P>
<P>
The Mexican president decorated 28 elderly teachers with the
"Ignacio Manuel Altamirano" medal for having taught for 50 to 63
years without interruption.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, thousands of teachers who came to the capital from
17 states held a demonstration today, demanding more pay. 
