Chilean state enterprise, can accept collaboration with foreign
enterprises to explore and exploit new copper mines.
</P>
<P>
During the talks, Li Lanqing relayed the greetings from Chinese
President Jiang Zemin and Premier Li Peng to Frei and said that
Frei's visit to China in November of 1995 promoted bilateral
relations.
</P>
<P>
Li, who headed a Chinese government economic and trade
delegation, arrived here on Wednesday evening for a 24-hour visit.
</P>
<P>
Chile is the fourth leg of Li's Latin American tour, which has
already taken him to Brazil, Cuba and Colombia. He will leave for
Argentina this afternoon. 
