<HEADLINE> Canada Welcomes NATO-Russia Pact </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
OTTAWA, May 15 (Xinhua) -- The Canadian government welcomed
today the conclusion of negotiations on a new framework for
NATO-Russia relations.
